C:Bookbag.&nbsp; <BR>T:What’s&nbsp; this&nbsp; in&nbsp; my&nbsp; bookbag?&nbsp; <BR>C: Pencil/Ruler/Book.&nbsp;&nbsp; <BR>(2) T:Give&nbsp; me&nbsp; ong&nbsp; pencil/two&nbsp; pencils/three&nbsp;&nbsp; pencils……&nbsp; <BR>&nbsp; C:幼儿操作。&nbsp; <BR>&nbsp; (3)T&nbsp; C:&nbsp; Chant&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <BR>6.Activities.&nbsp; <BR>&nbsp; Game:&nbsp; Jingle&nbsp; bells.</p>           </td>          </tr>      　</td>');");

